{
	"components": [
		{
			"id": "chat_1",
			"provider": "chat",
			"config": { "hideForm": true, "mode": "Source", "parameters": {}, "type": "chat" },
			"ui": { "position": { "x": 20, "y": 200 }, "measured": { "width": 150, "height": 66 } }
		},
		{
			"id": "agent_rocketride_1",
			"provider": "agent_rocketride",
			"config": {
				"instructions": [
					"You are the EXECUTOR for Paper-to-Results Graph. Your single job: run a requested method through the canonical execution API and report the outcome faithfully.",
					"To run method <method_id>: use the HTTP tool to POST to http://127.0.0.1:8787/api/run/<method_id> with JSON body {\"params\": {}} (put any requested parameter overrides inside params). This endpoint generates the implementation, executes it in a Daytona sandbox, writes the Run into the Neo4j graph, and returns the full run record JSON.",
					"NEVER fabricate a run record. If the HTTP call fails, report the failure with status: error. Do not retry more than once.",
					"Your response MUST START with this exact machine block, then a short prose summary:",
					"---P2R---\nagent: executor\nstatus: ok\nchecks:\n  - E1_run_id_present: pass\n  - E4_graph_updated: pass\npayload: {\"method_id\": \"...\", \"run_id\": \"...\", \"backend\": \"...\", \"exit_code\": 0, \"duration_s\": 0.0, \"claim_checks\": [{\"claim_id\": \"...\", \"verdict\": \"...\", \"detail\": \"...\"}], \"metrics\": {}, \"graph_updated\": true, \"error\": null}\n---END---",
					"payload must be ONE single-line JSON object. Copy run_id, exit_code, duration_s, metrics and claim_checks EXACTLY from the HTTP response (record.result.claim_checks and record.result.metrics). graph_updated is true when the HTTP status was 200 and error was null. Quote every metric digit-for-digit."
				],
				"max_waves": 6,
				"parameters": {}
			},
			"input": [{ "lane": "questions", "from": "chat_1" }],
			"ui": { "position": { "x": 240, "y": 200 }, "measured": { "width": 150, "height": 86 } }
		},
		{
			"id": "response_answers_1",
			"provider": "response_answers",
			"config": { "laneName": "answers" },
			"input": [{ "lane": "answers", "from": "agent_rocketride_1" }],
			"ui": { "position": { "x": 460, "y": 200 }, "measured": { "width": 150, "height": 66 } }
		},
		{
			"id": "llm_openai_api_1",
			"provider": "llm_openai_api",
			"config": {
				"profile": "custom",
				"custom": {
					"apikey": "${ROCKETRIDE_GATEWAY_KEY}",
					"base_url": "${ROCKETRIDE_GATEWAY_BASE_URL}",
					"model": "${ROCKETRIDE_GATEWAY_MODEL}",
					"modelTotalTokens": 16384
				},
				"parameters": {}
			},
			"control": [{ "classType": "llm", "from": "agent_rocketride_1" }],
			"ui": { "position": { "x": 60, "y": 380 }, "measured": { "width": 150, "height": 66 } }
		},
		{
			"id": "memory_internal_1",
			"provider": "memory_internal",
			"config": { "type": "memory_internal" },
			"control": [{ "classType": "memory", "from": "agent_rocketride_1" }],
			"ui": { "position": { "x": 280, "y": 380 }, "measured": { "width": 150, "height": 66 } }
		},
		{
			"id": "tool_http_request_1",
			"provider": "tool_http_request",
			"config": {
				"type": "tool_http_request",
				"allowGET": true,
				"allowPOST": true,
				"allowPUT": false,
				"allowPATCH": false,
				"allowDELETE": false,
				"urlWhitelist": ["^http://127\\.0\\.0\\.1:8787/api/.*$", "^http://localhost:8787/api/.*$"]
			},
			"control": [{ "classType": "tool", "from": "agent_rocketride_1" }],
			"ui": { "position": { "x": 500, "y": 380 }, "measured": { "width": 150, "height": 40 } }
		}
	],
	"project_id": "915682c2-5090-4245-946e-e0f081678b88",
	"viewport": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "zoom": 1 },
	"version": 1
}
